No. 595. Alfred Kessler et al., Petitioners, v. The Ensley Land Company et al. March 4, 1907. Mr. William A. Gunter and Mr. J. W. Baker for petitioners. Mr. John B. Knox for respondents.

Petition for a writ of certiorari to the United States Circuit Court of Appeals for the Fifth' Circuit denied.
